node.title: Good job boys. Stay safe everyone!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kimi Räikkönen on September 01, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and text.

node.text: This is it. This will be my last season in Formula 1. This is a decision I did during last winter. It was not an easy decision but after this season it is time for new things. Even though the season is still on, I want to thank my family, all my teams, everyone involved in my racing career and especially all of you great fans that have been rooting for me all this time. Formula 1 might come to an end for me but there is a lot more in life that I want to experience and enjoy. See you around after all of this! Sincerely Kimi
